::Kluster::

Kluster's eyes narrow, watching scan logs. KitKat had met with 
Megatron and Black Aracknia....

Tapping a few more keys on the console, Kluster orders the 
Cybertronain Fire to track Megatron's signature, swearing under his 
breath as he sees that he is at KitKat's base.

He was convinced that the meeting had something to do against the 
Maximals. They couldn't take on three Pred factions alone, not even 
with the CF. There could be some help though..

Kluster activates his comm, sending a long distance 
transmission, "Zardus, I need to speak with you."
